  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will collect data of patients who are treated with TACE followed by sorafenib for
      hepatocellular carcinoma (HCC) or patients without Sorafenib after TACE. In contrast to a
      prior observational study on sorafenib (GIDEON study), where pre-treatment with TACE was
      documented retrospectively, this study will collect more detailed information about the TACE
      treatment and the status of a patient when treatment with sorafenib is started.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
